smoke_test 1.1.0 (June 28, 2020)
================================

Feature additions
-----------------

    * Added the ``--error-code`` CLI argument.

smoke_test 1.0.2 (December 1, 2019)
===================================

Bugfixes
--------

    * Switched to "fake" libc headers, for improved compatibility with newer
      versions of GCC.

smoke_test 1.0.1 (September 2, 2019)
====================================

Bugfixes
--------

    * Migrated from Bitbucket (Mercurial) to GitHub (Git).

smoke_test 1.0.0 (December 17, 2018)
====================================

    * Initial release.
